title: Woman_Plus_Tree_2012_PL_English_subs.mp4
description:
An unfulfilled artist, his schizophrenic wife and a teenage son suffering from prosopagnosia - in other words, a dysfunctional family of eccentrics in 1930s Europe comes together to overcome a common threat; a serial killer.

Written and directed: Adam Wojtek Joyce

Featuring: Katarzyna Francuz, Michal Orlowski, Piotr Mahlik

Soundtrack: Minuit De Lacroix

B/W + Color
Approx running time: 90 min
Year of production: 2012
Polish with English subtitles
Mature audiences - some nudity
